	<td>Past: The HOW reached out to the client during coordinated outreach in the Jungle.  The HOW asked the client where she had been.  The client responded by stating that she had been staying in Carlsbad before her stay in the Jungle in Escondido.  The client asked the HOW what her shelter options were.  The HOW informed the client that there was SUD treatment bed available but she would have to be willing to split up with her adult son.  The client responded by stating that she would not be willing to do that.  The HOW informed the client that there was also a chance that she could get into our Family Shelter as her son has a learning disability.  The client express interest in the opportunity and the HOW introduced her to Jeremiah Bellomy.  Jeremiah Bellomy informed the client that he needed her to provide proof of her sons learning disability.  The client was able to provide proof and Jeremiah Bellomy completed her and her sons paperwork for an intake today  at our Family Shelter.  The client was thankful that she is going to have a safe and warm place to stay. Present: Client is staying in vista by vista village dr client is seeking shelter no beds. Available at the timeI provided client with food and water Client says that she is in vista because of a friend that she knows .Plan: Get refer to shelter GoalGoal: Client will like to get permanent housing. </td>
