	<td>PAST-Went to hotel to check in on Jennifer Gray and her kids. Client, Zayden and Chacity were there upon arrival. I spoke with Jennifer about her and her children going into shelter at the South County Lighthouse. Client stated that she is very concerned and worried about Chacity and her behavior, that Chacity is running with the wrong crowd, not attending school and continues to use drugs and alcohol. Client stated that it would possibly be a good move to get Chacity out of the area. Client stated that she has never kicked Chacity out of the home (or whenever they were living). Client was emotional but said she would speak with the kids and be ready for us to pick them up in the morning. Jennifer said she has not spoken with Robert but that the kids have. Client has not asked for any resources for her or her children. PRESENT-Went to hotel to pick up client and son. We helped client to move her belongings into the vehicle, upon leaving a man (Justin-ONC) stopped by and spoke with Jennifer. I questioned the man's presence and the son replied that he stopped by occasionally during their stay at the hotel. Client stated that Chacity did not return back to the hotel after her and client had an argument about the client's phone being used. Client stated that the police were called but Chacity had fled the scene upon arrival. Zayden said he saw Chacity by Walmart, and she appeared to be giddy and ok. Client stated that Chacity did not attend school today. We transported client to Madison Middle school where she withdrew Anastasia from school. Madison put Anastasia on independent for 15 days till transportation is managed for Anastasia. Anastasia's counselor gave her some resources and tools that are available for her. Kay will arrange communication and transportation for Anastasia and Chacity to resume attendance at their schools. Kay stated that the RBV social worker has been working with Chacity for about 2 years and that the family Chacity (Chacity's best friend's family) is with today will continue to support Chacity till further notice. I will inform Client with an update regarding this matter. PLAN-SDRM focus on getting clients shelter, clothing, transportation fixed and/or transportation assistance and other resources for the family.</td>
	<td></td>
	
</tr>




