	<td>Past : showed up to the office today 10/22/25. Client stated they got accident from South County lighthouse for drug paraphernalia. Client was honest with a situation. Client lost his wallet and phone. Client also talked to social worker on talks about sobriety working a program, client will stop by tomorrow 10/23/25 and go to DMV to obtain another ID card. Hopeful that client get back on track.Present: picked up client from his mother house where he is currently staying and took to DMV. Should be receiving ID in two weeks. Client will show back up here Tuesday 10/28/25 for goodwill rÃ©sumÃ© building meeting. Confident the client can remain sober and continue working on his progress for ERF housing.Goal: get client, a stable, part-time job, and into ERF housingPhase 1: obtain ID card(client already had drivers license)</td>
